    <item>
      <title>美联储降息预期受阻，美元升至一个月高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/dollar-rises-to-highest-in-a-month-as-fed-rate-cut-bets-stall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国经济的强劲表现粉碎了美联储近期调整政策的任何希望，彭博美元指数有望创下自 2 月份以来最长的周线上涨势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/dollar-rises-to-highest-in-a-month-as-fed-rate-cut-bets-stall</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 16:35:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
