      <title>BlueBay 希望购买瑞士信贷债务，押注新兴市场贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/bluebay-looks-to-buy-credit-suisse-debt-as-em-loan-bet-pays-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大皇家银行 BlueBay 资产管理公司一位高管向彭博新闻社表示，该公司有意购买瑞士信贷集团的新兴市场债务，因为该公司在发展中国家的企业贷款获得了强劲回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/bluebay-looks-to-buy-credit-suisse-debt-as-em-loan-bet-pays-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 11:17:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据和中国暂停购买导致金价两年来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/china-s-pboc-halts-gold-purchases-after-price-hits-record-in-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国一份重要就业报告意外强劲，粉碎了人们对美联储将很快开始降低借贷成本的希望，黄金价格创下两年多来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/china-s-pboc-halts-gold-purchases-after-price-hits-record-in-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:06:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业市场稳健，盈利前景看好，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份稳健的就业报告帮助平息了人们对经济放缓可能损害美国企业的担忧，即使这意味着美联储降息可能会推迟，股市也随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 22:42:28 GMT</pubDate>
